column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.psfMag_u, p.psfMag_g FROM #upload u, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(p.ra,p.dec,#) as N, SpecObj as s JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID where p.objID = N.objID and sqrt(s.ra*s.ra+s.dec*s.dec)<=N.distance ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
